GitHubManager - Class in edu.ncsu.csc.githubmanager.manager
The GitHubManager program allows you to: (1) assign students to GitHub teams and repositories by providing a formatted input file of repository assignments; and (2) update permissions (read, write, admin) for GitHub teams When assigning repositories, students are added to GitHub teams that have the same name as the GitHub repository they will be assigned.
